snippet.title: Minecraft Godzilla DLC
snippet.description: It’s time to meet the king of monsters in the new Godzilla adventure world by Team-KYO and Impress! Select the Godzilla film you fancy best. Play your way by escaping Godzilla’s wrath or even destroying the city as the blocky beast itself. Play solo or with friends, collect cool mementos from the movies, and don’t forget to head to the Dressing Room for your free Godzilla T-shirt!
